'''Muḥyeddin Ibn Ɛarabi''', s [[taɛrabt]] محي الدين ابن عربي, yettwasen kan s yisem n '''Ibn Ɛarabi''', d amedyaz, d amusnaw n ajjed, u wayen umi neqar ''[[Mystisism]]''. D yiwen ger ibabaten n tasnakta [[Taṣufit]]. Ilul deg usegas n 1165, di Mursi, tamurt n Andaluz, di Sbanya.<ref>http://www.wdl.org/en/item/7437/</ref> Imut deg 1240, di Dimecq, tamurt n Surya n tura. Qaren-as daɣen « Cix amuqran », isɛa azal n 846 n yidlisen. Deg isefra ines, yettmeslay-ed af tayri, cbaḥa, iba, aramsu, atg.

Asmi isɛa 14 isegasen, imlal di Kurdu (Sbanya) akw d [[Averroès]], sɣur ilmed aṭas n tmusniwin d tfiluṣufit.

